==Esperanto==
===Etymology===
From interrogative and relative pronouns of French (''[[qui]]''), Italian (''[[che]]'')

===Affix===
[[Category:Esperanto prefixes]]
'''ki-'''
# wh-, what. (Interrogative/relative [[:Category:Esperanto correlatives|correlative]] prefix.)
===Derived terms===
* ''[[kiu]]'': '''what''' individual, [[who]]
* ''[[kio]]'': '''what''' object, [[what]]
* ''[[kia]]'': '''what''' kind of
* ''[[kies]]'': belonging to '''whom''', [[whose]]
* ''[[kiel]]'': '''what''' manner/degree, [[how]]
* ''[[kie]]'': '''what''' place, [[where]]
* ''[[kiam]]'': '''what''' time, [[when]]
* ''[[kiom]]'': '''what''' quantity, [[how much]]
* ''[[kial]]'': '''what''' reason, [[why]]